data.description: Price improvement!!! OPEN HOUSE Sunday February 18th, 11AM-1PM. We'll maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home close to the Sequoia Park Zoo and Henderson Center. Remodeled kitchen complete with new cabinets, backsplash, and quartz countertops.  Newer Lopi wood stove and furnace. Berkdale 14x8 shed added in 2021. The oversized front yard includes a mature apple tree and ample space for parking or allows room for a garage with a second unit above.  The property also offers a fully fenced backyard and a large storage shed and deck off the family room.
